window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Logan Gyre is king of Cenaria, a country under siege, with a threadbare army and little hope. He has one chance - a desperate gamble, but one that could destroy his kingdom.</p> <p>In the north, the new Godking has a plan. If it comes to fruition, no one will have the power to stop him.</p> <p>Kylar Stern has no choice. To save his friends - and perhaps his enemies - he must accomplish the impossible: Assassinate a goddess.</p> <p>Performed by Dylan Lynch, Eric Messner, David Coyne, Thomas Penny, Andy Clemence, Michael Glenn, Mort Shelby, Tim Getman, Colleen Delany, Ren Casey, Laura Quinn, Elizabeth Jernigan, Yazmin Tuazon, Richard Rohan, Nanette Savard, Ken Jackson, James Konicek, Lilly Beacon, Joe Brack, Casie Platt, Christopher Graybill, Terence Aselford, James Lewis, Scott McCormick, Johann Dettweiler.</p>"; 
